=== potion of healing ===
qty=1 identified buc=blessed -> a blessed potion of healing
qty=1 identified buc=uncursed -> an uncursed potion of healing
qty=1 identified buc=cursed -> a cursed potion of healing
qty=1 identified buc=buc_unknown -> a potion of healing
qty=1 unidentified -> a milky potion
qty=1 called=heal? -> a potion called heal?
